Package textTranslator

Interface Summary
TranslatorInterface Every translation class will implement this interface
 

Class Summary
DetabTranslator Replaces tabs at the beginning of each line.
DoubleSpaceTranslator Replaces each newline in the input with two newlines
EntabTranslator Replaces each group of four spaces at the beginning of each line with a tab character.
FixIndentationTranslator Given a Java (or Java-like) program, indent it properly.
FlowTextTranslator Flows text (the way web pages do)
IdentityTranslator Makes no changes to the input.
SingleSpaceTranslator Replaces consecutive pairs of newlines with a single newline.
TextTranslator The main class, to show GUI, add translator, listen the action and perform the action.
WrapTextTranslator Wraps lines so that no line is longer than 72 characters.
